Kyle_Reese http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kyle_Reese 0 Kyle Reese is a fictional character in the Terminator franchise, who serves as one of the main protagonists in the first film with a supporting role in other works. The character is portrayed by Michael Biehn in The Terminator (1984) and Jonathan Jackson in Terminator: The Sarah Connor Chronicles (2008–2009); Anton Yelchin played him as a teenager in Terminator Salvation (2009), and Jai Courtney portrays him in Terminator Genisys (2015).
